title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: After exporting the data in the table, the expected result is that the data is successfully exported without any errors.
SR: To reproduce this issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Attempt to export the data from the table. 3. Observe the exception thrown while executing the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
